title: Google Chromes best new feature A mute button
text:
Google Chrome's best new feature: A mute button 
CNN Money Friday 23rd October, 2015 
ADSPACE-END --> The new feature comes in handy when you're listening to music or a watching a video in one tab, and all the sudden you start hearing audio from another tab you have open. The muted tab appears with an icon in the shape of a crossed-out speaker. This new feature is the latest in a long line of...
